modName: Bikini Trouble - UNP UNPB 7B MTM DG TopModel BBP BBPx TBBP
summary:
35 Bikinis Standalone Craftable (Three versions of each). With working weight slider.
UNP/UNP-BBP/UNP Skinny/UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx/7B/DG/UNP Topmodel and the sexy Vanilla body too (aka UNP Alpha)
Uses Linen and leather strips at the Tanning Rack(hide). Added Light Armor (upgradable) options.
descriptionHtml:
35 Bikinis Standalone Craftable. With working weight slider.

1.52 ESP's Changes crafting from forge to tanning rack. Update any main file with 1.52 ESP's

Uses linen and leather strips at the Tanning Rack (hide).
Optional updates for 1.52
Simply added a "z" to the name so it will be lowest on the list.
Light Armour (upgradable) options.
Optional world object,Â changes the world object to a basic bikini

Full Bikini Light Armour 18
Bikini Top Light Armour 9
Bikini Bottom Light Armour 9

Full Bikini uses biped 32
Bikini Top uses biped 32
Bikini Bottom uses biped 45

Same biped values that Brokefoot used for his Mashup.

Want to use a custom texture? It will replace the "Natural" version, place in here with these names.

[code]data/Textures/clothes/Bikini-Trouble/bikini.dds
data/Textures/clothes/Bikini-Trouble/bikini_n.dds[/code]


Use this for semi transparent texture. It will replace the "T-Natural" version.

[code]data/Textures/clothes/Bikini-Trouble/tbikini.dds
data/Textures/clothes/Bikini-Trouble/tbikini_n.dds[/code]

Note: The Vanilla (Bethesda) Body includes a nude version that all female NPC's use. It's needed for the full mod to work, If it isn't used only the full bikinis are "usable" without oddities. If you don't want to use it delete it in

[code]data/Meshes/actors/character/character assets/
femalebody_0.nif
femalebody_1.nif[/code]

Also, its highly recommended that you use a nude texture (UNP's work) and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3666]FemFeet by Phygit[/url]

Want more Bikinis? [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27758]Beads Bikini UNP by japantarou Fixed and UNPB also BBP BBPx TBBP[/url] I have it set-up the same as this mod.

Textures are from Rockslinger, crispiniscool, Rekicker, xs2reality, MrTroubleMaker, ff13, hagrid, lukie80 and dimon99

Original Mesh from dimon99, converted by me for UNP-BBP, UNPB, 7B, DG, TM and Vanilla (Bethesda) bodies

=======================================================================================================================================================

Bikini Trouble - CBBE Bodyslide conversion with optional TBBP support:

1) CBBE is required for this version of course, then:

2) Install Bikini Trouble first (any version)

3) Install the "Main" and "Various" packages for [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32731]Bodyslide CB Plus Plus[/url]

4) Optional - If you want to use the TBBP version, install [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34713]TBBP[/url]

5) You MUST generate the CBBE outfits in bodyslide++.exe (be sure to note TBBP vs. standard non-BBP version)

Please ask any questions about the CBBE version over at the Bodyslide CB Plus Plus page (linked in #3 above).
